A jiran wani zabe da zai sake ba shi damar cika matsayinsa a Kotun Koli, Trump yana neman tallafi ko tallafi don zaɓen tsakiyar lokaci a lokacin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar haɗarin rasa ikon Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a zaben Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia na yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya ganin shi a Intanet?
An shirya wa Trump yawon shakatawa a West Virginia don farawa a karfe 7 na yamma a yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya ganin taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar yawo a YouTube.
Da alama Trump zai jagoranci sauraron da ake yi wa babban kotun Brett Kavanaugh a wannan makon, har sai da Majalisar Dattawa ta sake amincewa da shi, wanda ya riƙe da kuri'arsa a lokacin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan zagaye na taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu wasu kuri'u a zaben watan Nuwamba.
