An shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau zai ba da damar ɗaukar hoto ga magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
