Daliban Harvard sun yi karatun yadda za su huta sosai.
A wannan shekara na jami'ar Harvard, ɗaliban karatun digiri na biyu za su yi barci sosai, don su yi ƙoƙari su fuskanci al'adun da ke ci gaba da fadadawa, waɗanda suke yin karatun su ta hanyar shan kofi a daren jiya.
Wani malamin ya lura cewa a cikin jami'o'i mafi kyau a duniya, ɗalibai suna rasa lada a matsayin hanya ta farko ta kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, malamin likitancin bacci a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard da kuma masanin asibitin Brigham da Women, ya tsara wannan hanya, wanda ya yi imanin cewa ita ce ta farko a Birtaniya.
Ta fara karatun ta lokacin da ta ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a lokacin karatun.
"A cikin wani yanayi, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, 'Me ya sa zan yi haka yanzu, a shekarar karshe na makaranta?
Ta ce babu wanda ya gaya mata muhimmancin samun barci mai kyau, kuma hakan ya ba ni mamaki", in ji Telegraph.
A cikin wannan karatun, wanda aka gabatar a farkon wannan shekara, an bayyana wa dalibai yadda yin barci mai kyau ke tasiri a kan karatunsu da kuma sakamakon wasanni, ban da inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin hauka a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard kuma darektan kula da lafiyar jami'ar, ya bayyana cewa jami'ar ta yanke shawarar ƙaddamar da karatun lokacin da ta ga ɗalibai ba sa barci sosai a cikin mako.
Wannan hanya ta tsawon lokaci ta ƙunshi abubuwa masu yawa.
A wani sashe, akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai ke danna tukunyar kofi, shinge, masu horarwa, da littattafai don ganin tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, da kuma tasirin rashin barci a wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin al'adun barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an bayyana wa mahalarta cewa rashin barci zai iya sa su kamu da ciwon zuciya, wanda zai iya kara yawan shan wahala daga ciki ko kuma ciwon daji.
A taswirar harabar makarantar, ta amfani da gumaka masu ma'amala, ana gayyatar masu halarta su yi tunani a kan al'adun yau da kullum.
Mun san cewa ba za mu canja al'adun ɗalibai ba.
"Amma muna ganin suna da hakkin su san, kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san abin da sakamakon shan taba zai kasance ga lafiyar ku", in ji Czeisler.
Har yanzu akwai al'adar alfahari da yin "karamin karatu", in ji shi, kuma matsin lamba da fasaha ta zamani da kuma ɗalibai ke yi a kan ɗalibai yana ƙara daɗa matsalar rashin karatu.
Ya ce, samun barci mai kyau, da barci mai kyau, ya kamata ya zama sirrin maganin damuwa, gajiya da tashin hankali -- kuma don samun nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa su ji yunwa, kuma za mu ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin kimiyyar halitta da kimiyyar halitta ya taimaka wa farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara darasin, kuma ya halarci ɗayan darussansa na farko a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ta ce wannan darasi ya buɗe idanunta kuma ya ƙarfafa ta ta shiga wani darasi da ya kasance wani ɓangare na harabar.
Kuma yana fatan mataki na gaba shi ne, ya nemi daliban su yi bincike na musamman kafin su shiga wata kungiya mai gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su saita ƙararrawa don sanin lokacin da za su kwanta, har ma da lokacin da za su farka, da kuma sanin tasirin tasirin hasken blue da hasken LED ke watsawa, wanda zai iya canza yanayin yanayin da ke cikin yanayin, kuma zai iya haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Meng ta ci nasara a kan sojojin Gerrard
Ranger sun sake fuskantar rashin nasara a kan aikin Dolly Meng'a wanda ya sa Steven Gerrard ya ci 1-0 a Livingston.
Daga Ibrox sun so su ci nasara a karo na farko bayan da suka ci 4-1 a St. Johnston a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holte ya jagoranci nasarar da ta gabata na tawagar Gerrard a wasan 18 na ta a matsayin koci, tare da maki takwas da ya samu daga shugabannin Landbrokes Championship Hearts da suka tsere ba tare da kulawa ba.
Meng'a ta zo da mu minti bakwai kafin lokacin hutu, kuma aikin Rangers bai kai ga wasan.
Yanzu 'yan wasan Rangers sun sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku kuma suna bin Hibernian ne kawai don ƙwallon ƙafa.
Wataƙila matsalar ta fi tsanani ga Rangers, domin an yi wa Calum Spence magani a kan wani rauni a kai, saboda wani abu da aka jefa daga waje ya buge shi.
Gerrard ya yi sauya-sauya takwas kuma ya sa ya isa rabin wasan kofin Ayr Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya tafi tare da shi zuwa Livi 11, wanda ya ci Heartsei maki a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da ganin yadda tufafinsa masu kyau suka shafe abokan hamayyarsa a kowane zagaye.
'Yan wasan Rangers sun karɓi dukiyar, amma Livingston ya fi amfana daga aikin su.
Dole ne a shigar da Scott Pittman na bangaren Mengas da Allan McGregor ya jefa amma dan wasan tsakiya bai yi amfani da damar ba.
Wani harbi mai zurfi na Keaghan Jacobs ya sami kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya samu damar fitar da shi daga baya.
'Yan wasan Rangers sun ci gaba da mulki, amma a cikin kashi na uku na ƙarshe, a wasan su, da alama cewa bege ya fi imani.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi tunanin cewa dole ne a yi hukunci a ƙarshen kwata lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo, amma alkali Steven Thomson bai kula da roko na Colombia ba.
Rangers sun sami nasarar harba harbi biyu kawai a farkon rabin, amma tsohon mai tsaron gida na Ibrox Liam Kelly bai sami matsala ba tare da kai na Lassana Coulibaly da kuma Ovie Ejaria mai sauƙi.
Wataƙila burin farko da Livi ya zira a minti na 34 zai iya lalata ci gaban wasan, amma babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan, idan aka yi la'akari da irin wannan ƙoƙari.
Har yanzu, Rangers sun kasa cin nasarar Jacobs a kan wani wasa na dakatar da kwallon.
Scott Arfield bai yi wani abu ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson kwallon, wanda ya zaɓa Menga a hankali don kammala shi a hanya mai sauƙi.
Gerrard ya shiga cikin hutu ta maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent, kuma canjin ya yi tasiri nan da nan lokacin da mai fage ya wuce Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban mamaki ya gudu ta hanyar layinsa don toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa 'yan wasan waje su yi wasa da suka fi so, Lithgow da Halkett suna yin wasa mai tsawo bayan dogon wucewa.
Ƙungiyar Holt ta sami damar kara samun nasara, amma McGregor ya riƙe shi da ƙarfi kafin ya yi wa kansa rauni daga kusurwar Lithgow.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers, Glenn Middleton, ya sake neman fansa a karshen lokacin da ya shiga cikin Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake sauraronsa.
Almanac: Wanda ya kirkiro Geiger Counter
Yanzu kuma ga wani shafi na "Sunday Morning" na Jamus: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka gabata, kuma kafin Denver, an haifi mai ilimin lissafi na nan gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya don ganowa da kuma auna radiation. Wannan shine dalilin da ya sa aka kira shi Geiger Count.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger Countdown ya zama iyakar kimiyya, kuma ya zama iyakar al'adun pop, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya ƙunshi Roy Rogers da Dale Evans cowboys, wadanda ba su da wata alama ga masana kimiyya:
Mutumin ya ce, "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne Geiger na'urar ƙidaya, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adinai masu radiation kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka wadannan belun kunne, zaka iya jin tasirin atomatik da ake samu daga radiation na ma'adinai".
Evans: "I, za a iya ji a yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, kwanaki kadan kafin ya cika shekaru 63.
