Alurar rigakafi tana koya wa tsarin rigakafi ya gane kwayoyin cutar a lokacin magani
Wannan hanya ta kasance ta cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya sannan kuma ta canza su a dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Sannan zasu iya ganin wani furotin wanda yake da yawa a cikin ciwon daji, sannan su sake yin allura.
Wannan rigakafin gwaji yana bada sakamako mai kyau ga marasa lafiya da ke fama da nau'ikan cututtukan daji daban-daban.
Wata mace da aka yi wa allurar rigakafi wadda ta koya wa tsarin rigakafi ya gane ƙwayoyin cuta, sun samu nasarar kawar da cutar kansa ta ƙwayoyin cuta fiye da watanni 18.
Wannan shine hanyar: cire kwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya, kuma a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje, don su iya "ganin" furotin da ake kira HER2 wanda ya saba da yawancin cututtukan daji, sannan su sake yin allurar kwayoyin.
Jay Berzofsky daga Cibiyar Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland ya ce, "Bincikenmu ya nuna cewa muna da maganin da zai iya kawo sakamako mai kyau".
Farfesa Berzofsky ya bayyana cewa, HER2 "yana sa ciwon daji ya karu a wasu nau'o'in", ciki har da na nono, na ovulation, na huhu, da na colon da na hanji.
Wani tsari na musamman da ya shafi yadda za a samu kwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya da kuma yadda za a samu kwayoyin cutar kansa daga cikin kwayoyin cutar, yana aiki a cikin maganin cutar sankarar jini.
