Tauraruwar wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ta yi magana game da namiji mai guba
Kit Harington ya fi shahara saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin mai safa Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na HBO na Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya nuna rashin amincewa da irin wannan jarumin mai tsattsauran ra'ayi, yana mai cewa saboda irin wannan takaddar a allon, matasa sukan ji cewa dole ne su kasance masu ƙarfi don a girmama su.
A cikin jawabinsa ga mujallar Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin an yi wani abu ba daidai ba kuma ya tambayi yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a lokacin #MeToo.
Kit kuma kwanan nan ya auri Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31 da haihuwa, tauraruwar Game of Thrones, kuma ta yarda cewa ta "yi imani" cewa dole ne ta magance matsalar.
'Na kaina, kuma da cikakken tabbaci, ina tunani a wannan lokacin - me muka yi da rashin mutunci?' in ji ta.
"Me muka koya wa maza a lokacin da suke girma, idan aka yi la'akari da matsalar da muke fuskanta yanzu?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama da alhakin karuwar namiji mai guba saboda yawan maza da aka nuna a cikinsa.
Ya ci gaba da cewa, 'Mecece halitta, kuma menene koyarwa?
