Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar za a yi bikin Global Citizen a New York, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke tattare da manyan masu fasaha da kuma babban manufa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A wannan karon da yake shekara ta 17, bikin na Global Citizen zai kawo dubban mutane zuwa Great Plains na Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don ƙara wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wato kawar da matsanancin talauci kafin shekara ta 2030.
An kafa bikin Global Citizen a shekara ta 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani shiri na tallafi na kasa da kasa wanda ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
Don samun tikitin kyauta don taron (idan ba ka shirya biyan tikitin VIP ba), waɗanda suke son halartar taron suna buƙatar yin ayyuka ko "aiki" kamar aika imel zuwa ga jagorar duniya, yin kira na waya, ko kuma yin kira ta wata hanya mai amfani don taimakawa wajen haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da manufar kawar da talauci.
Amma menene nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu a lokacin da ta rage mata shekaru 12 don cimma burinta?
Shin wannan ra'ayin na asali ne na karfafa mutane su yi wani abu ta hanyar wani shiri kyauta, ko kuma wani misali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism", wato, sa mutane su ji cewa suna yin canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan wani tsari na kan layi ko kuma yin tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" na mabiyanta, suna matsa lamba don cimma manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce shugabannin duniya sun tura su su sanar da manufofi da alkawuran da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 kafin shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyoyi sun ambaci alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukan, kuma aƙalla $ 10 biliyan an biya ko an riga an karɓa.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka ba su sun shafi mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Daga cikin manyan alkawuran da aka yi, akwai The Power of Nutrition, "ƙungiyar masu zuba jari da masu aiwatarwa da ke zaune a Burtaniya, waɗanda suka himmatu wajen taimaka wa yara su bunkasa iyakar damarsu". Ta yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don kawar da rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar, bayan ta karɓi fiye da 4,700 tweets daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa, da kuma 'yan Global Citizen kamar ku, za mu sanya rashin adalci na zamantakewar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin tarihi", in ji Jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, a gaban jama'a, a wani taro na rayuwa a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙari ga haka, ƙungiyar ta ce bayan da ta gudanar da ayyuka sama da 5,000 don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na iyaye mata da jarirai a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta ba da kuɗi ga aikin Power of Nutrition wanda zai taimaka wa mata da yara miliyan 5 ta hanyar ayyukan da suka shafi abinci mai gina jiki.
Da yake amsa wannan tambayar da suke da ita a shafin, me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa, "Wannan zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala, wani lokacin za mu fadi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar yadda muka yi a baya a manyan harkokin kare hakkin bil adama da kuma yaki da wariyar launin fata, za mu yi nasara, domin mun fi karfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monáe sun kasance a cikin wasan kwaikwayon na wannan shekara a New York. Deborah-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon.
