Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da yin amfani da tallace-tallace don kai hari
Bayan wani jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafuka hudu a cikin jaridar EU da ke nuna amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada labaransa.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ambaci karin kudin da jaridar Sin ta biya a cikin Des Moines Register, jaridar biyu mafi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, a ranar Laraba da ta gabata bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin shiga zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba. China ta musanta zargin.
Da ake zargi Beijing da kokarin shiga zaben Amurka, Trump ya yi watsi da abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa Reuters cewa wani sabon kamfen ne a Washington da ke ci gaba da bunkasa domin matsa lamba a kasar Sin.
Duk da cewa ba laifi ba ne gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu suna cikin wani yakin kasuwanci mai ci gaba wanda a cikinsa kowace kasa ta sanya ƙuƙwalwa a kan shigo da juna.
Kungiyar 'yan adawa ta kasar Sin, da ta tallafa wa jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump a farkon yakin kasuwanci, an yi tunanin cewa za ta kai hari ga fitarwa daga jihohi kamar Iowa, kamar yadda masana a kasar Sin da Amurka suka ce.
Terry Branstad, Jakadan kasar Sin na Amurka kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, wanda ke daya daga cikin jihohin da suka fi fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kuma harkokin kasuwanci lahani.
A cikin wani labarin da aka wallafa a jaridar Sunday's Des Moines Register, Branstad ya ce, "Sin ta kara daukowa ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu".
"Ta hanyar yada farfaganda, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin yada labarai da kuma 'yancin yada labarai ta hanyar sanya tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a nan a cikin gidan jarida a kan titi na Beijing, akwai ƙananan muryoyin masu ra'ayi na rashin yarda kuma ba a ganin ainihin ma'anar ra'ayoyi daban-daban da jama'ar Sin za su iya samu game da rikitarwa ta tattalin arzikin kasar Sin, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji ta.
Ya kara da cewa "daya daga cikin jaridu mafi shahara a kasar Sin ya kauce wa tayin buga labarinsa amma bai bayyana wane jarida ba.
