A kan takarar Kotun Koli, Ford ya bayyana cikakkun bayanai game da cin zarafin jima'i tun kafin ya ba da shaida a fili, masu bincike sun nuna cewa zai iya zama raguwa idan 'yan Republican sun yanke shawarar ci gaba da sakewa.
"Ya zama babban rikici ga Jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin kasa na Republican, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba batun zaben kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma ko Kavanaugh ya zauna a kan kujerar da ake tuhuma, amma yadda 'yan Republican suka magance wannan batu da kuma yadda suka bi da mata", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan ƙungiyar da ke taimakawa wajen zabar 'yan Democrat na USA.
Ko ta yaya, da alama Amurkawa sun rabu sosai tsakanin shaidun Ford da Kavanaugh a lokacin da suke yanke shawara ko su amince da su, amma da alama mutane da yawa suna goyon bayan na biyu.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu sauraro sun amince da shaidar Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin 100 sun amince da shaidar Kavanaugh.
