Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet don ya yi nasara da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, yana shirin kaddamar da wani shiri na farawa wanda zai yi nasara akan Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ya dogara ne akan dandamali na software na kyauta na Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da kuma wane mutum zai sami damar samun damar wannan bayanin.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya game da manufar Inrupt ta zama "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar "cikin bayanan sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyukan, kalandar, ajiyar kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify: duk suna aiki a cikin mai bincike guda ɗaya, kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Wani abu na musamman game da bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa yana cikin ikon mai amfani don samun dama ga wani nau'in bayanai.
Wannan shi ne abin da kamfanin ke kira "Sarrafa mutane ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce ta sanya albarkatu, matakai da kuma iyawa masu dacewa don taimakawa wajen sa Solid ya zama mai amfani ga kowa.
A wannan lokacin, kamfanonin sun hada da Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu tasowa da aka yi hayar su yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa "magana da Facebook da Google game da bukatar yin canji mai tsanani a lokacin da tsarin kasuwancin su ya canza sosai a kowace rana.
Ba mu tambayar su ba.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka buga a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "yana da manufa ta kafa tsarin halittu da makamashi na kasuwanci wanda zai taimaka wajen kare cikar da ingancin sabon cibiyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza shi gaba daya lokacin da ya kafa Intanet a cikin World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Har a lokacin da Inrupt ya fara aiki, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kafa da kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan zamani na gaba na Intanet", Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
