Saboda an katse hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun bayanai daga gwamnatin Donggala ba, wanda shine yankin da ya fi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5, arewacin Palou.
