Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da birnin Palu da kuma gwamnatin Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, kuma yana kan iyakar bakin teku na yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi; a shekara ta 2017, yawanta ya kai kusan 379,800.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala, a gefe guda, gwamnati ce da ke rufe yankin fiye da kilomita 300 (180 mil) na arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gwamnati, wanda shine gundumar gudanarwa a karkashin lardin, yana da yawan mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya ya dogara da kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar nikelin tana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne a Morowal, a gefen Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia (Indonesia National Board for Disaster Management), Paluk da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
